data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This 4-bedroom, 1.5-bath residence perfectly blends comfort and style, offering a truly exceptional living experience. Step inside to discover the warmth of beautiful hardwood floors flowing seamlessly throughout the bedrooms and the spacious living room. The heart of this home is the modern kitchen, featuring granite countertops and a suite of stainless steel appliances that are all yours to keep. Cooking and entertaining becomes a joy in this stylish and functional space. The well-appointed 1.5 bathrooms boast contemporary design and convenience, ensuring a delightful and efficient daily routine. Park easily in the generous 2-car garage, providing secure and convenient storage for your vehicles or additional space for your hobbies and projects. Venture outside to the expansive fenced-in backyard, a private oasis perfect for gatherings, play, or simply relaxing in the fresh air. Create lasting memories in this versatile outdoor space that accommodates your lifestyle. This home is not just a residence; it's a haven of comfort and sophistication. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours and celebrate every moment in a place you'll proudly call home. Schedule your showing today and envision the possibilities in this exceptional property!
